stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active
    Active --> Active: valid reports below threshold
    Active --> Sanctioned: transaction locks and rechecks threshold\nconsume reports once\ncreate one action and audit\nincrement auth_epoch for user
    Sanctioned --> Sanctioned: additional reports do not extend action
    Sanctioned --> Expired: db_now >= expires_at
    Expired --> Active: canonical status ignores expired action
    Active --> Sanctioned: only new unconsumed reports reach threshold

    note right of Active
      User is active or product is visible.
      Canonical DB-time service is authoritative.
    end note

    note right of Sanctioned
      Seven-day immutable action.
      User dormant or product hidden.
      HTTP, WS, chat, query, and report paths agree.
    end note

    note right of Expired
      Historical action and audit remain.
      No scheduler reversal and no physical deletion.
      Invalidated sessions require fresh login.
    end note
